Note: this patch is only valid when applied to the nntp 1.5.11t5 distribution
      available from  ftp.uu.net:news/nntp/nntp-t5.tar.gz      

This patch adds the following to the NNTP 1.5.11t5 server:

  o  XMOTD command to display a news message of the day file from server.
     Syntax:  XMOTD 921231 235959

  o  XUSER command to log tin clients username to nntp logfile.
     Syntax:  XUSER Iain Lea

  o  HELP command changed to list the extensions.

  o  XINDEX & XOVER extensions are standard in the nntp 1.5.11t5 distribution.

For compile & install instructions read the file INSTALL.NNTP

Enjoy 

  Iain
 
